  | `dip`     | delete inside parentheses       | **d**elete **i**nner **p**arens |
  | `dib`     | delete inside braces            | **d**elete **i**nner **b**lock |
  | `dit`     | delete inside tag               | **d**elete **i**nner **t**ag |
  | `d$`      | delete to end of line           | **d**elete to `$`          |
  | `d0`      | delete to start of line         | **d**elete to `0`          |
  | `dgg`     | delete to start of file         | **d**elete to **gg**       |
  | `dG`      | delete to end of file           | **d**elete to **G**        |
  | `dt{c}`   | delete until char {c}           | **d**elete un**t**il       |
